11 November 2014The Special Envoy to Nigeria, Minister Jeff Radebe will brief members of the media on the outcomes of the meetings held with the government of Nigeria.This is part of government s commitment to keep the South African and Nigerian public abreast on the repatriation of the mortal remains of the victims of the Nigeria building collapse.The details of the briefing are as follows: Date: Today, Tuesday - 11 November 2014Time: 18h00, Nigerian time (19h00 South African time)Venue: Inter-Continental hotel (Lagos, Nigeria) Media RSVPs:Themba Thobela (Nigeria, Lagos) Cell: +2773 504 3841/ 073 504 3841 E-mail: Themba@gcis.gov.zaEnquiries:Phumla Williams Spokeswoman for the Inter-Ministerial Task Team Cell: +2783 501 0139/ 083 501 0139Issued by Department of Communications